import React from "react";
import OutNavbar from "./components/NavBar/OutNav";
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Link, Switch, Route } from "react-router-dom";
import Home from "./components/BeforeLoginPages/Home.js"
import Solutions from "./components/BeforeLoginPages/Solutions.js"
import Pricing from "./components/BeforeLoginPages/Pricing.js"
import ContactUs from "./components/BeforeLoginPages/ContactUs.js"
import Login from "./components/BeforeLoginPages/Login.js"

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
        <OutNavbar/>
        <Switch>
        <Route path="/" exact>
            <Home />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/Solutions" exact>
            <Solutions />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/Pricing" exact>
            <Pricing />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/ContactUs" exact>
            <ContactUs />
        </Route>
        <Route path="/Login" exact>
            <Login />
        </Route>
    </Switch>
    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
